name: Sun Logo Tank Top - Navy Blue
description: Printed on Gildan 100% Cotton Jersey. The Circle K Logo is represented from the animation that is played at the beginning of KODACHROME videos. The back delivers KODACHROME's mission statement in exposing the talent within every dancer. The tank top is a comfortable fit for summer and athletic wear. This is a fashionable apparel for dancers with ambitions to improve their talents and promote an inspiring message.
